# HTTP Client Rules
ALWAYS_USE_AXIOS=true  # Always use Axios instead of fetch for HTTP requests
AXIOS_INSTANCE_PATH=src/lib/axios.ts

# Explanation:
# - fetch is not preferred because:
#   1. Inconsistent error handling across browsers
#   2. No built-in request/response interceptors
#   3. Manual JSON parsing required
#   4. No request cancellation
#   5. No upload progress monitoring
#
# - Instead, use the Axios instance from src/lib/axios.ts which provides:
#   1. Consistent API across browsers
#   2. Automatic error handling
#   3. Request/response interceptors
#   4. Automatic JSON transformation
#   5. Request cancellation
#   6. Upload/download progress monitoring 